lead_paragraph: Bill Hamid made a save on a breakaway in the 90th minute, Jared Jeffrey scored in stoppage time and D.C. United tied Real Salt Lake 1-1 on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Hamid Has Late Save, Jeffrey Scores in 92nd; United Ties RSL
